msgctxt "1224"
msgid "Prison Guard"
msgstr "Guardia de Prisión"

msgctxt "1228"
msgid "Yakuza Inmate"
msgstr "Prisionero yakuza"

msgctxt "1232"
msgid "Talk_No"
msgstr "Talk_No"

msgctxt "84_Prison Guard"
msgid "C'mon. Slip me a couple million and I'll make it worth your while."
msgstr "Vamos. Dame un par de millones y haré que tu tiempo haya valido la pena."

msgctxt "96_Yakuza Inmate"
msgid "Gimme a break, man. Ya been hittin' me up for cash every month since I got tossed in this dump. I ain't made of money."
msgstr "Gimme a break, man. Ya been hittin' me up for cash every month since I got tossed in this dump. I ain't made of money."

msgctxt "108_Prison Guard"
msgid "What's the big deal? You scratch my back, I scratch yours."
msgstr "¿Cuál es el problema? Tú me rascas la espalda, yo rasco la tuya."

msgctxt "120_Yakuza Inmate"
msgid "Yeah, but you scratchin' my back's gonna end up bleedin' me dry... Fine. I'll get one of my pals on the outside to wire it over tomorrow."
msgstr "Yeah, but you scratchin' my back's gonna end up bleedin' me dry... Fine. I'll get one of my pals on the outside to wire it over tomorrow."

msgctxt "132_Prison Guard"
msgid "Heh, pleasure doing business. Don't worry, I'll make sure you're taken care of real good."
msgstr "Je, un placer hacer negocios. No te preocupes, me aseguraré de que te cuiden muy bien."

